    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Nagisavelia hikarui sp. nov. 1, 3, 5, male; 2, 4, 6, female. 1, Holotype; 2–6, paratypes. 1–3, Dorsal aspect; 4, ventral aspect. 5–6, Live specimen. Scale refers to 1–4." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10010397/files/figure.png" ;
