<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10010399>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–10. Nagisavelia hikarui sp. nov. and its type locality. 7, Adult male; 8, adult female; 9, type locality; 10, habitat." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10010399/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10010403>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11–14. Abdominal segment VIII, pygopore, and proctiger of Nagisavelia hikarui sp. nov. male, holotype. 11, Abdominal segment VIII, ventral view; 12, proctiger, dorsal view; 13, pygophore (segment IX) and proctiger, lateral view; 14, same, dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10010403/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10010407>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–18. Head, second gonocoxa, ovipositor and gynatrial complex of Nagisavelia hikarui sp. nov. female. 15, Head, ventral view; 16, second gonocoxa and gonoplac; 17, ovipositor (first gonapophysis), ventrolateral view; 18, gynatrial complex. Scale bars = 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10010407/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10010410>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19–24. Scanning electron microscope (SEM) photographs of Nagisavelia hikarui sp. nov. 19–22, Male; 23–24, female. 19, 23, Head to abdomen; 20, thorax and abdomen, 21, eye, lateral view; 22, hind tibia and tarsus; 24, abdomen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10010410/files/figure.png" ;
